</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/FiremanSam" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/FiremanSam">Fireman Sam</a></em> had one called <em>In Action</em> that was comprised of three acts. It was also released to home video with an additional segment where the actor who played Sam visited kids in a park.
