</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/TheMuppetShow" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/TheMuppetShow">The Muppet Show</a></em>
</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/MyLittlePony" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/MyLittlePony">My Little Pony</a></em> (There was one based on Generation 3 in the late 2000s, and one based on <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/MyLittlePonyFriendshipIsMagic" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/MyLittlePonyFriendshipIsMagic">Friendship is Magic</a> that was supposed to tour in 2020, but was cancelled due to production delays and scheduling conflicts)
