<h2 class="bold font-l">Progressive on Ice</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
This Progressive commercial parodies the idea of making an ice show out of a beloved property... not that it's stopping people from wishing it was real. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
