<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">Progressive on Ice</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
This Progressive commercial parodies the idea of making an ice show out of a beloved property... not that it's stopping people from wishing it was real.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="8gumo7">
<input type="hidden" name="is_logged_in" value="0">
<p>How well does it match the trope?</p>
<div id="star-rating-group">
<div class="trope-rate">
